            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining roasted garlic paste </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and <strong>mayo</strong> in a bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>roasted garlic aioli</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
