    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one pot chicken breast paella</strong> drizzled with the <strong>roasted garlic aioli</strong></p><p>To garnish, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> roughly over the paella with scissors</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
